race.description: Bet365 Same Race Multi Race Maiden Plate
race.comment: Tricky and the race day betting will be instructive. INSAIN HARRY (17) resumes and has switched barns. Placed 6/9 in a deep initial preparation, and he's looked sharp in his two Flemington jumpouts. Riordan sticks aboard from those, and he maps well enough. He's been nudged out in stronger races and shapes as the one to beat. DYNAMITE DANCER (3) had prepared well and found a place at Warrnambool on debut. He's sure to keep improving and can make the finish with average luck in the run. SALIZOU (14) debuts and won her most recent jumpout. Yendall rides and will give her every chance from an inside gate. KINGS COMMISSION (2) creates interest resuming off a long break for the Hawkes yard. He has the ability, but has been very much a work in progress. He's been gelded, and his recent jumpouts suggest he's on track. Has a low gate, and the betting will tell plenty with him.
